page.title: 20CUSTOMS- OUR "FAMOUS" SONG
page.content:
Our version of Ilkley Moor Bar Tat. Sung to the same tune.
V1.Where st bin this last three weeks? On Ilkley and Burley Moor. V2.What has't tha done upon the Moor? Walked and walked and walked. V3.What did tha find upon tha Moor? Crowberry, bracken and heather. V4 What did tha see upon the Moor? Stone and cup ring markings. V5.What did tha collect upon the Moor? Beetles, moss and snails. V6.What did tha hear upon the Moor? Shots from the rifle range. V7.How many sheep upon the Moor? Far too many to count. V8.What's all the information for? The Domesday Project.
